OL,3,CGuernsey Budget: Vape tax and fuel
OL,4,Cduty rise but deficit sits at #48m
OL,6,FGuernsey's government will operate
OL,7,Fwith an overall deficit of #48 million
OL,8,Fif its 2026 Budget is approved.
OL,10,FThis means the island's government
OL,11,Fwill continue to spend more than it
OL,12,Freceives in revenue.
OL,14,FWith comprehensive tax reforms due to
OL,15,Fbe debated later next year, the
OL,16,Fisland's biggest revenue-raising
OL,17,Fmeasures - corporate tax and the
OL,18,Fproposed introduction of a Goods and
OL,19,FServices Tax (GST) - are currently
OL,20,Funder review.
