OL,6,FThis means very few real-term changes
OL,7,Fare being laid out by the Budget
OL,8,Fdocument.
OL,10,FThe President of Policy and Resources,
OL,11,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez, says,
OL,12,F"It's important to distinguish between
OL,13,Fthe 2026 budgeting process - where
OL,14,Freally I don't think it would be
OL,15,Fworthwhile, as we don't have the time,
OL,16,Fto implement anything fundamental.
OL,18,F"It's really important that these
OL,19,Fconsiderations are looked at
OL,20,Fcomprehensively and in their correct
OL,21,Fcontext."
