OL,6,FIn a statement last month, P&R's Vice
OL,7,FPresident, Deputy Gavin St Pier,
OL,8,Fcalled many of these submissions
OL,9,F"unaffordable", stating that "no one
OL,10,Fis getting everything they asked for"
OL,11,Fin the Budget.
OL,13,FHowever, in the Budget document, P&R
OL,14,Fconcedes that "expenditure requests
OL,15,Fdeemed essential, or where costs are
OL,16,Falready being incurred, have been
OL,17,Fincluded".
OL,19,FThe initial cash limits for Committees
OL,20,Fhave therefore been increased by #12
OL,21,Fmillion.
